<p><strong>标题：</strong>SCP-2894-JP - 梦想<br />
<strong>作者：</strong>©︎<span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/kossy" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(5670836); return false;"><img class="small" src="https://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=5670836&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1604484684" alt="kossy" style="background-image:url(https://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=5670836)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/kossy" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(5670836); return false;">kossy</a></span><br />
